hal terpenting dalam hidupku.

573
00:26:21,106 --> 00:26:25,211
Tapi bagaimana kalau bukan?

574
00:26:25,243 --> 00:26:28,314
Bagaimana jika aku membuang
hal terpenting bagiku?

575
00:26:31,784 --> 00:26:34,821
Ya, aku memikirkan hal yang sama.

576
00:26:34,854 --> 00:26:36,557
Kulihat Dina hari ini.

577
00:26:37,723 --> 00:26:40,059
<i>Mike sepertinya pria baik-baik.</i>

578
00:26:40,093 --> 00:26:42,295
Ya.

579
00:26:42,327 --> 00:26:44,230
Ya, dia memang baik.

580
00:26:47,066 --> 00:26:48,835
Ayah benar-benar mengacaukan kita?

581
00:26:48,867 --> 00:26:50,869
Ya. Sangat.

582
00:26:58,243 --> 00:27:01,914
<i>Fokus. Ingat, kehidupan seorang
